    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014I've babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and honestly, there isn't a single scratch on it. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell! I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
