    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade BMW E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero paint correction required, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Interior smells new. Full service history included.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
