    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original deep luster with no swirling, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
