      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been maintained to a showroom standard. This motorcar underwent a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical perfection, offering the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. An uncompromising choice for those who demand the finest quality available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
