    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch, a spotless interior, and it runs like a total dream. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know someone is going to be so happy behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and fall in love with it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
