    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated inline-six engineering. Featuring the iconic S54 powerplant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, the mechanical synchronicity is flawless. The chassis is structurally optimized with reinforced subframe mounts, and the variable M differential lock provides surgical power delivery through the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, with the high-pressure VANOS system and rod bearings fully serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. This is a museum-quality example with zero deferred maintenance and impeccable factory paint depth.",
